creator: Darbu
descriptionHtml:
Music streaming library with access to music created by the artists from the state of Mizoram. You can stream from vast collection of songs in the library or purchase new releases that are exclusive to the platform. You can share, socialize and interact with artists and other users within the platform.

You can also support your favourite artists by purchasing their merchandise which will be available exclusively on the platform.
descriptionShort: Hyper-local audio and music streaming platform
